WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.010 --> 00:00:02.640 
Jack bends wire to create unique sculptures.

2
00:00:03.370 --> 00:00:05.660 
He bent a large piece into a tree shape

3
00:00:05.670 --> 00:00:08.420 
last week and has bent countless wires
for his art.

4
00:00:08.990 --> 00:00:12.260 
His dog sometimes bites his materials, playfully.

5
00:00:13.190 --> 00:00:15.240 
It bit a rubber tube yesterday but has

6
00:00:15.250 --> 00:00:16.980 
bitten nothing important so far.

7
00:00:17.570 --> 00:00:20.540 
The wind blows strongly in Jack's outdoor studio.

8
00:00:21.190 --> 00:00:25.600 
It blew his sketches away last month and
has blown through his workspace all summer.

9
00:00:26.650 --> 00:00:30.320 
Occasionally, a balloon in Jack's
installations bursts unexpectedly.

10
00:00:31.070 --> 00:00:35.620 
One burst during an exhibition opening
last night and has burst twice this week.

11
00:00:36.210 --> 00:00:38.800 
He catches falling objects skillfully.

12
00:00:39.370 --> 00:00:41.520 
He caught a delicate glass piece mid -air

13
00:00:41.530 --> 00:00:44.320 
yesterday and has caught many items
before they could break.

14
00:00:45.070 --> 00:00:47.400 
Jack deals with challenges creatively.

15
00:00:48.210 --> 00:00:50.600 
He dealt with a supply shortage last year

16
00:00:50.610 --> 00:00:53.500 
and has dealt with various obstacles
throughout his career.

17
00:00:54.290 --> 00:00:56.680 
Jack digs in his garden for inspiration.

18
00:00:56.690 --> 00:00:59.620 
He dug up some interesting rocks last

19
00:00:59.630 --> 00:01:02.400 
spring and has dug many holes for his
outdoor sculptures.

20
00:01:03.050 --> 00:01:05.680 
He fights to preserve local art spaces.

21
00:01:06.430 --> 00:01:08.680 
He fought against a gallery closure last

22
00:01:08.690 --> 00:01:11.180 
month and has fought for artists' rights
for years.

23
00:01:12.150 --> 00:01:13.760 
Jack hangs his works carefully.

24
00:01:14.410 --> 00:01:16.760 
He hung a major piece in the City Museum

25
00:01:16.770 --> 00:01:19.560 
last week and has hung exhibitions in
various venues.

26
00:01:23.850 --> 00:01:28.500 
He hid a large sculpture under a tarp
yesterday and has hidden many works in

27
00:01:28.510 --> 00:01:29.960 
progress from curious eyes.

